 after becoming president hargis led a recordsetting fundraising initiative he has a bold vision of creating a modern landgrant university that combines disciplines to better prepare students for a new world prior to becoming president of osu hargis had a distinguished banking and legal career and led many active civic and philanthropic initiatives hargis was a candidate for the republication nomination for governor of oklahoma in  and is familiar to many oklahomans through the political perspective and wit he provided on the awardwinning television program “flashpoint” a firm believer in the power of imagination and collaboration hargis was the first chair of the oklahoma creativity project which seeks to catalyze a culture of creativity in culture commerce and education hargis and his wife ann have two married children and three grandchildren v burns hargis  oklahoma city ok  intelius sign in we found v burns hargis in oklahoma city ok v burns hargis intelius found that v burns hargis from oklahoma city ok we have connected them to  addresses  phones and  relatives or associates also known as burns b hargis burns v hargis get report now v has lived in oklahoma city ok stillwater ok vs relatives matthew hargis vaden hargis ann hargis v burns hargis professional status president at university of oklahoma get report now want to know more about v get a comprehensive background report find full phone numbers and other contact information when available all from billions of available public records continue below for more details about v or use our people search engine to find others get background check on v burns hargis get a criminal check on v burns hargis get a public record report on v burns hargis get a people search report on v burns hargis v burns hargiss contact information known cities lived in find out where v burns hargis has lived as well as v burns hargiss phone numbers and email addresses v burns hargis has lived in  states oklahoma address for v burns h