 joining bank of oklahoma in  hargis practiced law in oklahoma city for  years most recently with the firm of mcafee  taft he is a former president of the oklahoma county bar association former president of the oklahoma bar foundation and is a fellow of the american bar foundation hargis served as vicechairman of the oklahoma state election board the oklahoma constitutional revision commission and served as chairman of the oklahoma commission for human services he is a former member of the commission of the north central association of colleges and schools hargis was a candidate for the republican nomination for governor of oklahoma in  a firm believer in the power of imagination and collaboration hargis was the first chair of the oklahoma creativity project he has served and chaired many boards including the board of regents for the oklahoma agricultural and mechanical colleges of oklahoma state university hargis received the state’s highest honor when he was inducted into the oklahoma hall of fame in  hargis and his wife ann have two married children and three grandchildren   petition · v burns hargis big  expansion · changeorg skip to main contentstart a petitionbrowsemembershiplog in my petitionssettingslog outstart a petitionmembershipsearchlog in or sign uplog indont have an account sign uplog in with facebookorforgot passwordby joining or logging in via facebook you accept changeorg’s terms of service and privacy policy petition closedpetitioning v burns hargis and  othersdecision makersv burns hargisdavid borengregory l fenveskenneth winston starrvictor j boschini jrduane nellisbernadette graylittlesteven leathe gordon geekirk schulzbig  expansionkenny johnson united stateskenny johnsonunited statessupportersthis is a petition to the leaders of all the big  schools asking for them to expand the big  back to  teams the big  is at a disadvantage with the college football playoffs if they do not expand and create a conference title game the big  needs to expand